{"title":"个人博客","date":"2023-03-27T13:57:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年3月27日","L":"2023/03/27","MM-DD":"03-27"},"author":"可乐mono","thumbnail":"https://image-1301698134.cos.ap-chengdu.myqcloud.com/obsidian/202303310241640.jpg","link":"2023/03/27/个人博客","comments":true,"tags":["博客"],"categories":["学习笔记"],"updated":"2023-03-31T07:42:51.036Z","content":"<p>如何使用hexo框架搭建个人blog</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<h1 id=\"个人博客搭建步骤\">个人博客搭建步骤<a title=\"#个人博客搭建步骤\" href=\"#个人博客搭建步骤\"></a></h1>\n<h1 id=\"第一步、安装-node\">第一步、安装 node<a title=\"#第一步、安装-node\" href=\"#第一步、安装-node\"></a></h1>\n<ul>\n<li>找到网站安装</li>\n<li>检查 node 和 npm 版本</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">node -v</span><br><span class=\"line\">npm -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"第二步、安装-hexo-框架\">第二步、安装 hexo 框架<a title=\"#第二步、安装-hexo-框架\" href=\"#第二步、安装-hexo-框架\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>利用 npm 安装 cnpm</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">npm install -g cnpm --registry-https://registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>检查 cnpm 版本</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cnpm -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>利用 cnpm 全局安装 hexo</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cnpm install -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>检查 hexo</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"第三步、利用-hexo-安装博客\">第三步、利用 hexo 安装博客<a title=\"#第三步、利用-hexo-安装博客\" href=\"#第三步、利用-hexo-安装博客\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>建立一个博客文件夹</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">mkdir 可乐的博客</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>初始化 hexo</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo hexo init</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>hexo</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo n</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo clean</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo g</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo d</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo s</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"第四步、托管到-github\">第四步、托管到 github<a title=\"#第四步、托管到-github\" href=\"#第四步、托管到-github\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>github 创建同名仓<br>\n<img src=\"https://image-1301698134.cos.ap-chengdu.myqcloud.com/obsidian/202303272215841.png\" alt=\"image.png|375\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>安装发布插件</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">cnpm install --save hexo-deployer-git</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>_ config. yml 中设置<br>\n<img src=\"https://image-1301698134.cos.ap-chengdu.myqcloud.com/obsidian/202303272222817.png\" alt=\"image.png\" loading=\"lazy\"></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">type: git</span><br><span class=\"line\">repository: https://github.com/yourname/merelinker.github.io.git</span><br><span class=\"line\">branch: main</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>发布</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo clean</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo g</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"西医综合大纲","link":"2023/04/03/西医综合"},"plink":"http://colamono.top/2023/03/27/个人博客/","toc":[{"id":"个人博客搭建步骤","title":"个人博客搭建步骤","index":"1"},{"id":"第一步、安装-node","title":"第一步、安装 node","index":"2","children":[{"id":"第二步、安装-hexo-框架","title":"第二步、安装 hexo 框架","index":"2.1"},{"id":"第三步、利用-hexo-安装博客","title":"第三步、利用 hexo 安装博客","index":"2.2"},{"id":"第四步、托管到-github","title":"第四步、托管到 github","index":"2.3"}]}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"可乐mono","link":"<a href=\"http://colamono.top/2023/03/27/个人博客/\" title=\"个人博客\">http://colamono.top/2023/03/27/个人博客/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"},"reading_time":"234 字约 2 分钟"}